Package: olympicAthletes
Type: Package
Title: Olympic Athlete Event Data, Athens 1896 to Milano-Cortina 2026
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chester", "Ismay",
           email = "chester.ismay@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A tidy, long-format dataset of every athlete-event participation
    in the modern Olympic Games, spanning Athens 1896 through Milano-Cortina
    2026 (about 315,000 rows). Extends the rgriff23 'Olympic_history' dataset
    (1896-2016) with five additional editions scraped from olympedia.org:
    PyeongChang 2018, Tokyo 2020, Beijing 2022, Paris 2024, and
    Milano-Cortina 2026. Companion datasets cover edition-level metadata
    and verified medal tables for every edition from 1896 to 2026.
